{"tid":583512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解應該坐關愛座嘅人死都唔肯坐關愛座","createTime":"2018-03-07T05:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:36:22.000Z","uid":42971,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19f4f523cd44034c18243affee8bf60db2740629","tid":583512,"uid":42971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"返學放學都搭地鐵,次次都見到啲老人家衝入嚟搶凳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係好得意架窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地死都唔肯坐關愛座係都要搶嗮啲普通位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後班後生嘅又怕坐咗關愛座會仆街,結果永遠都係關愛座無人坐,成班人企嗮係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心班廢老就坐翻關愛座喇<br />\n強烈要求設置非關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n65歲或以上廢老唔準坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要坐就坐關愛座喇屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3921caa29075bb1f7f86695dc043e5869e5ba28e","tid":583512,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"果堆寫住優先座係代表要優先坐果到 <br />\n唔應該亂坐"},{"pid":"50e62ff8f951c33505f4e14bffee82110b2e2ef7","tid":583512,"uid":42971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3921caa29075bb1f7f86695dc043e5869e5ba28e","tid":583512,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"果堆寫住優先座係代表要優先坐果到 <br />\n唔應該亂坐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/face